import React, { useState } from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import api from "../Backendroutes"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; function AddPatient() { const [form, setForm] = useState({ isOldPatient: false, docType: "OPD Registration", uhidNo: "", opdNo: "", date: "", time: "", casualty: "No", patientName: "", guardianName: "", houseNo: "", street: "", village: "", district: "", gender: "", maritalStatus: "", aadharNo: "", bloodGroup: "", mobile: "", email: "", dob: "", age: "", }); const handleChange = (e) => { setForm({ ...form, [e.target.name]: e.target.value }); }; const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); try { const res = await axios.post(api.addpatient.url, form); if (res.data.success) { toast.success("Patient Registered"); } else { toast.error("Something went wrong"); } } catch (error) { toast.error("Server error"); } }; return (

Patient Registration

); } export default AddPatient;
